    <div class="hearder">
        <div class="sqs-block-content">
            <h1>Willing to help Neighbours?</h1>
            <p class="signup-text my-5">
                You are amazing! Thanks for caring for your neighbors. Before you fill out the form, some things for
                you to
                know:<br><br>

                Please do not worry if you do not know your whole schedule right now. We know things are changing
                rapidly for
                everyone.
                Go ahead and sign up, and you can update us once you start receiving requests.<br><br>

                We do ask that you help us protect our vulnerable community members by only volunteering if you are
                in good
                health. We
                ask that you:<strong> feel healthy, display no coronavirus symptoms, have not traveled out of the
                    country or
                    come into contact
                    with a sick person in the past 14 days, and practice continuous social distancing.</strong>

                We will reach out with a message as we receive requests in your zip code, At that point, you will
                have the
                chance to
                confirm your availability (hooray!), and we will give you more details and connect you directly with
                the person
                who
                requested the delivery.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="container">
        <h3>Before starting as a volunteer there are some points which a volunteer should keep in mind</h3>
        <div class="list-group my-4">
            <button type="button" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
                Not affected from coronavirus
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">Not travelled from any affected
                countries in the last 14 days </button>
            <button type="button" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">Always wear mask and gloves at the time
                of delivery</button>
            <button type="button" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">Delivery of essential items like milk,
                medicines must be as early as possible.</button>
            <button type="button" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">Free from any symptoms related to
                coronavirus</button>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex;justify-content: center;">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button"><a style="color: white;" href="/signUp">Get
                    Started</a></button>
        </div>

    </div>
